CustomField.description: ANZARD defines a cleavage embryo as an embryo that is one to four days old, after fertilisation. For embryo donation/provision cycles, use this data item to record the number of vitrified cleavage- stage embryos donated/provided. If fresh embryos are being donated/provided, use the N_EMBDON_FRESH data item instead.
CustomField.label: ANZARD - Number of cleavage-stage embryo
